level.heading: Designation of the Effi Slaughter Barry HIV/AIDS Initiative.
level.text: The East of the River HIV/AIDS Capacity Building Initiative administered by the Department of Health shall be known as the Effi Slaughter Barry HIV/AIDS Initiative ("initiative").
